{"tid":2375691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"11..11大三罷 向路軌擲物及拒捕判囚8個月　中大女生刑期上訴遭李運騰駁回","createTime":"2021-01-22T08:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T08:26:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6dce7cf067f002d2bfd1383b6eb77caa2de9b33","tid":2375691,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571816-20210122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571816-20210122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=d242599a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571816-20210122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f6afab2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571816-20210122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n前年11月11日有人發起「大三罷」，一名中大女生被控當日在大埔港鐵路軌投擲竹枝及拒捕，早前被判囚8個月。她不滿刑期，在高等法院提出上訴，被法官<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">李運騰</span></span></strong>駁回。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人透過律師說，原審裁判官沒有考慮社會服務令，沒有適當地考慮感化主任正面建議。<br />\n<br />\n但法官在判辭中形容，刑期已是相當寬大，甚至可以說是略低，若非上訴人背景良好和年輕等，還打算上調刑期。"},{"pid":"399e0fb209ea44980425c149b9ac3897b464f7da","tid":2375691,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}